                    <p class="text-slate-700">Total cost: $14-$20 per sq ft installed</p>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-slate-600 mb-3 leading-relaxed">
                    When we encounter foundations with extensive penetrations, stone foundations, or irregular surfaces where sheet membrane would require excessive piecing, we switch to liquid-applied membranes. Tremco TREMproof 250GC provides a truly seamless monolithic barrier that self-flashes around every pipe, conduit, and protrusion.
                  </p>
                  <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                    <strong>Trade-offs:</strong> Higher material cost and longer installation time (multiple coats, curing between coats), but the seamless application eliminates the #1 failure point in sheet membrane systems: seams and terminations.
